  • About

Southpac Service is a professional migration consulting firm with headquarters in Sydney, Australia. Our firm has a single focus: to provide the best migration advice in the industry in order to get our clients the visa they want.

We’ll use our knowledge and experience to simplify the migration process, make sure your application package is perfect, and provide the best presentation of your case to the Department of Immigration and Border Protection (DIBP) or the MRT or RRT review tribunals. And if you’ve had a refusal or cancellation, we’ll sort it out and show you all your options – one of our specialties is solving immigration problems, no matter how difficult or complex. We’ll fight hard to get you the outcome you want.

But our work only begins when we lodge your visa application or appeal – after that we’re in close contact with the Department, and will handle all communications with the Department on your behalf, keeping you up to date 24/7 with all updates on your case.

Today we live in a technology-driven world – our technology takes the entire visa application process online, and lets you communicate directly with the Registered Migration Agent assigned to your case. And we’ve simplified the visa application process so you only fill out one form – we’ll do the rest.

What makes us different?

Knowledge – Migration law and regulations are constantly changing, and our knowledge of current migration laws and regulations is first-rate. We publish Australia Visa News, a weekly newsletter that clients and others in the industry use to keep up to date on the latest migration law and regulation changes.

Experience – We’re highly experienced with many visas including the latest legislation for employment, skilled, partner & family, student, visitor visas and others. As a Australian Registered Migration Agent, all of our work is conducted under a strict code of conduct.

Transparency – We charge fixed fees so you can be confident of costs with no surprises. During your case you’ll know everything happening with your case 24/7 through our secure Client Portal.

Results – We use our knowledge and experience to deliver what matters in the end: results. We’ll work hard to get you the visa you want.
